### Cooldown System
#### Overview
A cooldown system prevents an action from being performed too frequently.

#### Code Example
```python
import time

class Cooldown:
    def __init__(self, duration):
        self.duration = duration  # duration in seconds
        self.last_used = 0

    def can_use(self):
        return time.time() - self.last_used > self.duration

    def use(self):
        if self.can_use():
            self.last_used = time.time()
            return True
        else:
            return False

# Example usage:
cooldown = Cooldown(10)  # 10-second cooldown

while True:
    if cooldown.use():
        print("Action performed!")
    else:
        print("Cooldown not ready yet.")
    time.sleep(1)
```

